<br>
Sure, gear is more important for meeles than for casters but I am still quite crippled if I don't have my gear since 40% of my mana and Hp's comes from it, not to mention resists.<br>
<br>
Caster loot is much more rare than melee loot. No it is not fair. A caster likes a new toy just as much as the next fellow.<br>
